data.description: Welcome to your coastal escape in Historic St. Andrews, Florida. This 5-bedroom, 3.5 bathroom, 3,300 square foot home is a dream come true, offering unmatched beachside living with dedicated beach access on St. Andrews Bay just Steps away! This home features vaulted ceilings with beams, creating an elegant and inviting atmosphere. With three stories, this property offers distinct living areas, providing both privacy and flexibility to suit your lifestyle. The home boasts over 1600 square feet of wrap-around porches and covered outdoor spaces, perfect for enjoying the coastal breeze and entertaining guests. Two sets of French doors off the main living area, French doors off the master bedroom, and a private balcony off the upstairs bedroom flood the interior spaces with natural light and connect seamlessly to the beautiful outdoor areas. A private entrance on the first floor opens the door to rental income opportunities, making this property ideal for investors or those looking to offset their expenses. The Opportunity to Own in Gwaltney Estates is very rare, Don't Let This Chance Slip Away. Schedule Your Private Showing Today! Exterior Photos will be added Tuesday due to weather
